# Data Schema

## Users Collection (`Users/{uid}`)
| Field       | Type    | Required | Notes                          |
|------------|---------|----------|--------------------------------|
| email      | string  | yes      |                                |
| firstName  | string  |          |                                |
| lastName   | string  |          |                                |
| admin      | boolean |          | Default false                  |
| developer  | boolean |          | Default false                  |
| isActive   | boolean |          | Default true                   |
| role       | string  |          | e.g. 'user'                   |
| userUID    | string  | yes      | Same as doc id                 |
| createdAt  | string  |          | ISO date                       |
| lastLogin  | string  |          | ISO date                       |
| streak     | number  |          | Login streak count             |

## Consistency
- Use `userUtils.ensureUserDoc` when creating new users
- Use `??` for defaults when reading (e.g. `userData.admin ?? false`)
